      {
        date: '2025-09-26',
        content:
          '基于 <a href="https://github.com/withastro/astro" target="_blank">Astro</a> 和 <a href="https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure"target="_blank">Astro Theme Pure</a>开始重新搭建博客'
      },
